      {
         "recipeDescriptionLine":"Honey Glazed Chicken is a delightful dish that is a perfect blend of savory and sweetness. The entire dish can be prepared in 45 mins."
      },
      {
         "recipeDescriptionLine":"It tastes best with chicken wings and thighs. Boneless chicken can be used as well to make this dish."
      }
   ],
